property="og:title" content="Sell My Scrap Car Montreal &amp; Toronto | Auto CA"/><meta property="og:description" content="Free towing, same-day pickup, instant cash offer for scrap and junk cars in Montreal &amp; Toronto. Get your quote in 60 seconds."/><meta property="og:url" content="https://autoca.ca"/><meta property="og:site_name" content="Auto CA"/><meta property="og:locale" content="en_CA"/><meta property="og:type" content="website"/><meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image"/><meta name="twitter:title" content="Sell My Scrap Car Montreal &amp; Toronto | Auto CA"/><meta name="twitter:description" content="Free towing, same-day pickup, instant cash offer for scrap and junk cars in Montreal &amp; Toronto."/><meta name="next-size-adjust"/><script src="/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js" noModule=""></script></head><body><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"AutoDealer","@id":"https://autoca.ca/#organization","name":"Auto CA","image":"https://autoca.ca/opengraph-image","telephone":"+1-514-217-6588","email":"info@gtadigitalsolutions.com","priceRange":"$$","address":{"@type":"PostalAddress","streetAddress":"6965 Rue Saint-Jacques","addressLocality":"Montreal","addressRegion":"QC","postalCode":"H4B 1V3","addressCountry":"CA"},"url":"https://autoca.ca","openingHours":["Mo-Fr 09:00-19:00","Sa 09:00-17:00","Su 11:00-16:00"],"areaServed":["Montreal","Toronto","Laval","Longueuil","Mississauga","Brampton"],"aggregateRating":{"@type":"AggregateRating","ratingValue":"4.9","reviewCount":"127"}}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"Service","serviceType":"Scrap and Junk Car Buying","provider":{"@id":"https://autoca.ca/#organization"},"areaServed":[{"@type":"City","name":"Montreal"},{"@type":"City","name":"Toronto"},{"@type":"City","name":"Laval"},{"@type":"City","name":"Longueuil"},{"@type":"City","name":"Mississauga"},{"@type":"City","name":"Brampton"}],"description":"Auto CA buys scrap, junk, and damaged cars in Montreal and Toronto with free towing, same-day pickup, and instant cash offers.","offers":{"@type":"Offer","priceCurrency":"CAD","description":"Free cash quote for scrap and junk cars, towing included."}}</script><script type="application/ld+json">{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"How much will you pay for my scrap car?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Auto CA pays between $100 and $5,000+ for scrap and junk cars in Montreal and Toronto, depending on the year, make, model, weight, and condition. Newer or heavier vehicles and those with reusable parts fetch the most. Fill out our 60-second form and we call you back within 30 minutes with a firm, no-haggle cash offer."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Does the car need to run to sell it?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"No. We buy cars in any condition — running or not. Dead engines, accident write-offs, flood damage, missing parts, blown transmissions, and fully scrapped vehicles are all accepted. If it has four wheels (or even if it doesn't), we will make you an offer."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Is towing really free?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. Free towing is included with every purchase across Montreal, Toronto, and surrounding areas. There are no hidden pickup fees, no deductions from your quote, and no charge if your car is in a garage, driveway, or street. The price we quote is the cash you receive."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"How fast can you pick up my car?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Most pickups happen the same day or within 24 hours. After you accept your offer, we schedule a time that works for you — often within a few hours in Montreal and the Greater Toronto Area — and pay you cash on the spot when we tow it away."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What documents do I need to sell my scrap car?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"You generally need your vehicle registration and a valid photo ID matching the registered owner. In Quebec we handle the SAAQ transfer paperwork; in Ontario we manage the MTO transfer. Our team walks you through everything and completes the documentation for you at pickup."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can you buy cars with a lien or outstanding loan?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In some cases, yes. If there is a lien or active loan on the vehicle, contact us with the details and we will explain your options. Often the payout can be applied toward the remaining balance. We assess each situation individually before confirming the offer."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Do you service all areas in Montreal and Toronto?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes. We cover the entire island of Montreal plus Laval, Longueuil, Brossard, and the South Shore, as well as Toronto, Scarborough, North York, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Brampton, Vaughan, Markham, Ajax, and Pickering. If you are nearby, just ask and we will confirm coverage."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I sell a car without the title or ownership?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Possibly. A title or ownership document makes the sale fastest, but if it is lost we can often still buy the vehicle once we verify you are the legal owner with ID and registration. Reach out and we will tell you exactly what we need for your situation."}}]}</script><div style="font-family:system-ui,&quot;Segoe UI&quot;,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,&quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;,&quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;;height:100vh;text-align:center;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center"><div><style>body{color:#000;background:#fff;margin:0}.next-error-h1{border-right:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.3)}@media (prefers-color-scheme:dark){body{color:#fff;background:#000}.next-error-h1{border-right:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.3)}}</style><h1 class="next-error-h1" style="display:inline-b