crapped vehicles are all accepted. If it has four wheels (or even if it doesn't), we will make you an offer.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is towing really free?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Free towing is included with every purchase across Montreal, Toronto, and surrounding areas. There are no hidden pickup fees, no deductions from your quote, and no charge if your car is in a garage, driveway, or street. The price we quote is the cash you receive.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How fast can you pick up my car?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Most pickups happen the same day or within 24 hours. After you accept your offer, we schedule a time that works for you — often within a few hours in Montreal and the Greater Toronto Area — and pay you cash on the spot when we tow it away.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What documents do I need to sell my scrap car?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"You generally need your vehicle registration and a valid photo ID matching the registered owner. In Quebec we handle the SAAQ transfer paperwork; in Ontario we manage the MTO transfer. Our team walks you through everything and completes the documentation for you at pickup.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can you buy cars with a lien or outstanding loan?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"In some cases, yes. If there is a lien or active loan on the vehicle, contact us with the details and we will explain your options. Often the payout can be applied toward the remaining balance. We assess each situation individually before confirming the offer.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do you service all areas in Montreal and Toronto?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. We cover the entire island of Montreal plus Laval, Longueuil, Brossard, and the South Shore, as well as Toronto, Scarborough, North York, Etobicoke, Mississauga, Brampton, Vaughan, Markham, Ajax, and Pickering. If you are nearby, just ask and we will confirm coverage.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I sell a car without the title or ownership?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Possibly. A title or ownership document makes the sale fastest, but if it is lost we can often still buy the vehicle once we verify you are the legal owner with ID and registration. Reach out and we will tell you exactly what we need for your situation.\"}}]}"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"9:{\"fontFamily\":\"system-ui,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,\\\"Apple Color Emoji\\\",\\\"Segoe UI Emoji\\\"\",\"height\":\"100vh\",\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"display\":\"flex\",\"flexDirection\":\"column\",\"alignItems\":\"center\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"}\na:{\"display\":\"inline-block\",\"margin\":\"0 20px 0 0\",\"padding\":\"0 23px 0 0\",\"fontSize\":24,\"fontWeight\":500,\"verticalAlign\":\"top\",\"lineHeight\":\"49px\"}\nb:{\"display\":\"inline-block\"}\nc:{\"fontSize\":14,\"fontWeight\":400,\"lineHeight\":\"49px\",\"margin\":0}\n10:[]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"0:[\"$\",\"$L4\",null,{\"buildId\":\"bknE90YuPm6-ZhCexWM1B\",\"assetPrefix\":\"\",\"urlParts\":[\"\",\"_not-found\"],\"initialTree\":[\"\",{\"children\":[\"/_not-found\",{\"children\":[\"__PAGE__\",{}]}]},\"$undefined\",\"$undefined\",true],\"initialSeedData\":[\"\",{\"children\":[\"/_not-found\",{\"children\":[\"__PAGE__\",{},[[\"$L5\",[[\"$\",\"title\",null,{\"children\":\"404: This page could not be found.\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"style\":{\"fontFamily\":\"system-ui,\\\"Segoe UI\\\",Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif,\\\"Apple Color Emoji\\\",\\\"Segoe UI Emoji\\\"\",\"height\":\"100vh\",\"textAlign\":\"center\",\"display\":\"flex\",\"flexDirection\":\"column\",\"alignItems\":\"center\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\"},\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"style\",null,{\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":